Let's imagine that we want to describe a book so this would include mentioning things like the title

48

00:03:16.410  -->  00:03:17.670
the name of the author.

49

00:03:17.700  -->  00:03:25.860
The number of pages the code for the description list element is simply DL.

50

00:03:25.860  -->  00:03:30.920
Now let's begin with the title of this imaginary book inside a DL element.

51

00:03:30.930  -->  00:03:32.620
